{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_16", "eventName": "反常光譜", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "EG-8", "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "往事", "storyInfo": "一座沉沒的城市重見天日，一盞廢棄的礦燈再度亮起。這年頭太怪了，什麼事都有可能發生。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g5_deepmine", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "轟炸……轟炸停止了。", "name": "膽小的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們、我們走吧，好嗎？不是去地上，而是繼續從下面走，趁那些炸彈還沒炸到我們這裡——", "name": "膽小的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1", "posfrom": "0,-50", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……起來，尤里，還有其他人。我們得去找雷爾金，還有他說的那個地方。", "name": "憂慮的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們的兄弟姐妹中，勇敢的那些都跟雷爾金去佔領崗哨了。", "name": "憂慮的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在轟炸停下來了，上面不知道是什麼情況。如果還想見到他們，就只能上去。", "name": "憂慮的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "去幫他們，或者像雷爾金說的那樣，去記住他們。走不動的就用手、用礦鎬，爬也要爬上去。", "name": "憂慮的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是雷爾金把他的礦燈託付給我們——", "name": "膽小的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那你記得他說了什麼嗎？", "name": "憂慮的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他……他什麼也沒說……", "name": "膽小的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這就對了，他什麼也沒說。這和他們留下的那些物資沒什麼區別，只是一份保障。", "name": "憂慮的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也可以選擇把它留在這裡，就像……一個提醒。", "name": "憂慮的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，提醒。把礦燈放進礦車裡吧，就放在我們過來的時候一路推著的那輛。", "name": "憂慮的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……如果有人會來……", "name": "憂慮的礦工"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "尤里，我記得你會寫字。", "name": "憂慮的礦工"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_papertear", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這本工作日誌後面是空白的，不用白不用。", "name": "憂慮的礦工"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來。我說，你寫。", "name": "憂慮的礦工"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣，如果有人來，他們至少會知道這裡發生過什麼事。", "name": "憂慮的礦工"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_iceforest_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$suspenseful_intro", "key": "$suspenseful_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>烏薩斯北原，某礦場</><p=2>1101年冬</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_both", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 2.0}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_094", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "長……長官大人，請問我們現在……要去哪裡？", "name": "病重的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_094"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這好像不是回廠裡的方向——", "name": "病重的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_094"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_082"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "閉嘴，繼續往前走。", "name": "衛兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_082"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快走！", "name": "衛兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_082"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）礦場又停工了。", "name": "懷疑的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）挖不出東西……加工廠裡就沒有原材料。", "name": "懷疑的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）如果上面用不到這麼多人手了，我們會被帶去哪裡？", "name": "懷疑的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "連病得最重的那幾個都被趕出來了，半個礦場的人都在這裡……", "name": "恐慌的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不想走了，我不想死！", "name": "恐慌的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（小聲）小聲一點！", "name": "懷疑的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "集團軍士官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "穿過樹林，去湖邊。那裡，是你們的墓地。", "name": "集團軍士官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在抵達之前，不要妄想……", "name": "集團軍士官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "自己能夠逃走。", "name": "集團軍士官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "深林中，不斷有厚重的軍靴踩在雪地上，前進著，也催促著。"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "礦工們的“護送者”不僅僅只有隊伍前面這幾位。"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_snow_2", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.6, "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowbootwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就到這裡，停下來。", "name": "集團軍士官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "開始吧。", "name": "集團軍士官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_082"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人都站到冰面上去。", "name": "衛兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_082"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，長官大人，我不想——", "name": "恐慌的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1970_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.5, "r": 1.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_broadswordblood", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-50", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "軍刀將她的話語和脖頸一起割斷，血液夾雜著熱氣噴濺在軍人的盔甲上。"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了烏薩斯的榮光。", "name": "集團軍士官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_094"}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天……天啊……", "name": "病重的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_094"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "繼續。", "name": "集團軍士官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_082"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "後、後面的人，趕快補上她的空位，快點！", "name": "衛兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_082"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_surfacefrozen", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "sur"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "sur", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……我們為什麼要遭受這樣的對待？", "name": "懷疑的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 129, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_082"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別*烏薩斯粗口*廢話——", "name": "衛兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_082"}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "難道陛下的承諾都是假的嗎？我們的命還不如一隻馱獸有分量嗎？", "name": "懷疑的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告訴我——", "name": "懷疑的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "集團軍士官"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1978_1#1$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在軍人再度抬手的瞬間，地面的震顫也終於能夠為人所感知。"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "起先只是細微的斷裂，來自湖面，來自地下，而後是如骨牌倒塌般的連鎖反應。"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_erthshkng", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "e"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 4.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 90.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "e", "fadetime": 6.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_surfacefrozen", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大地顫動，湖心塌陷，逐日累積的地形變化終於引起質變。它吞噬冰面上的感染者，也吞噬即將對他們行刑的劊子手。"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "跑——快跑！！", "name": "懷疑的礦工"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1969_1#1$1"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_snowrun", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "200,0", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "趁衛兵也愣住的瞬間，礦工甩開對方的鉗制，往來時的方向跑去。"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天災——", "name": "驚恐的礦工"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是天災！！", "name": "驚恐的礦工"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_thunders_amb", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.03, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_erthshkng", "volume": 1.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "e"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 4.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 90.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "e", "fadetime": 6.0}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spirlstrsndlss", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_rockfall", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "士兵，礦工；加害者，受害者。廣闊的安加拉湖包容了所有，又送出了所有。"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塌陷的冰面之下，一座古老的移動城市隨地形的變化驟然上升，衝破冰封，終於得以重見天日。"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而在那上面……舊式建築群、死者相貌猙獰的屍骨，都仍保留著它們沉入水底時的模樣。"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g10_tent_inside", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "animtext", "attributes": {"content": "<p=1>烏薩斯遠北，災後重建區域</>", "id": "at1", "name": "group_location_stamp", "style": "avg_only_heavy", "pos": "-400,-200", "block": "false", "p": 1.0}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "animtextclean", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“北原”……“天災”……“湖”……", "name": "勤奮的礦工"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這麼一小塊地方，這麼多詞，我只知道三個。", "name": "勤奮的礦工"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "慢慢來，你總有一天都會知道的。", "name": "青年工匠"}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的課程對我來說太基礎了。現在礦井沒人管理，我打算把那份工作接下來，再想辦法去學一門修鞋以外的手藝。", "name": "青年工匠"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等戒嚴解除，我要去聖駿堡。", "name": "青年工匠"}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不想去聖駿堡，我只想讀書。每天學會三個詞，一週就是二十一個，一個月就是……", "name": "勤奮的礦工"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_highheelfts", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_415_1#1$1", "duration": 1.5, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我很高興看到你們始終懷有一顆向上的心。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "需要我的幫助嗎？", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#1$1"}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些詞，女士，它們還是讓我糊塗。", "name": "勤奮的礦工"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_415_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "相信你說的是這些“名詞”，對嗎？因為這是我們這週的課程——“認識名詞”。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#1$1"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“名詞”——對，名詞！我好像已經能分辨出來了，但還沒辦法確定它們的意思。", "name": "勤奮的礦工"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "比如這個……“腮門刻”……是什麼意思？", "name": "勤奮的礦工"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_415_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦……", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#1$1"}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它讀作“塞夢珂”。就像上一行裡的湖叫“安加拉”，也像你叫“沃瓦”一樣，它只是一個名字。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#1$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一座移動城市的名字。", "name": "卡謝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_415_1#1$1"}, {"id": 209, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "66_g5_deepmine", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_energywell", "volume": 0.0, "loop": "true", "channel": "en"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.8, "channel": "en", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "告別了同伴，青年下到礦井中，準備開始工作。"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "礦道無人維護就會損壞，礦井無人看管就可能會發生坍方。至少在他離開這裡之前，他不會允許以上兩件事情發生。"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "青年舉著礦燈開始巡邏。他仔細地查看所有軌道，直到發現一輛明顯不屬於這裡的礦車，出現在其中一條岔路上。"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_openftstpwalk", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……這是……", "name": "青年工匠"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "礦燈？", "name": "青年工匠"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有一封信——", "name": "青年工匠"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "青年工匠"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一場抗爭……曾在這裡醞釀？", "name": "青年工匠"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天啊。提出礦區互連的人來過這裡！他們想佔領那個有駐軍的崗哨！", "name": "青年工匠"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我就知道，那不是憑空捏造……", "name": "青年工匠"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "channel": "en", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "66_i20", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"xScaleFrom": 1.05, "yScaleFrom": 1.05, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cndlbrn", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_churchfire", "loop": "true", "channel": "a", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 2.0, "channel": "a"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……", "name": "青年工匠"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論這是誰的燈，它都被保存得很好，還能點亮，只是上面有些灰塵……", "name": "青年工匠"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也許我應該把它帶走，帶去聖駿堡——", "name": "青年工匠"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……然後讓所有人看看……", "name": "青年工匠"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這盞沒有名字的礦燈，和那些沒有名字的人。", "name": "青年工匠"}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "en", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "a", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}